  "text": "17 th October, 2001 Notification No. 65/2001 - Central Excise (N. T.) In exercise of powers conferred by rule 9 of the Central Excise (No.2) Rules, 2001, the Central Board of Excise and Customs hereby makes the following amendments in the Ministry of Finance (Department of Revenue), notification No. 35/2001-Central Excise (N.T.) dated the 26 th June, 2001, namely: - In the notification, - (a) for Annexure-I, the following shall be substituted namely: - Form A- 1 Application Form for Registration (b) for Annexure-II, the following shall be substituted namely: - Form A- 2 Registration Certificate Note : You must have the latest version of Acrobat Reader to read these forms. Download Acrobat Reader 2. This notification shall come into force on 1st November, 2001. -- 1 of 1 --",
